channel.title: WebClient problem
channel.description:
I have problem on WebClient like title says... [img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/21566242/nimet%C3%B6nr.png[/img]
If i open the webclient page this get's stuck on "starting up".. and if i open the client.jar file this works withnout problems...
the WebClient.html code = [code] <HTML> <HEAD> <TITLE>WebClient</TITLE> <META HTTP-EQUIV="PRAGMA" CONTENT="NO-CACHE"> </HEAD>
<BODY>
<applet name="Client" width="765" height="503" archive="client.jar" code="client.class"> <param name="java_arguments" value="-Xmx1024m"> </applet>
</BODY> </HTML> [/code]
